00:20:10,292 --> 00:20:14,505
<i>Sial. Kenapa si pecundang itu
tiba-tiba tampak keren?</i>

435
00:20:15,131 --> 00:20:17,341
<i>Hentikan. Aku sudah gila.</i>

436
00:20:20,094 --> 00:20:23,013
Kak, ritsletingmu terbuka.

437
00:20:23,097 --> 00:20:26,684
Kak, ritsletingmu terbuka.

